    <div style="min-height:135px; padding-top:30px; font-size:16px;">
        The purpose of the FAC is to promote constructive, open and two-way communications between all of the franchisees and the management of Planet Fitness.  The goal of the FAC is to facilitate communication and build value within the Planet Fitness franchise system; promote the interchange of ideas among and between Planet Fitness franchisees; and otherwise improve and facilitate communication between and among Planet Fitness and itâ€™s franchisees for the purpose of improving and strengthening the System, the Planet Fitness brand, and increasing sales at Planet Fitness franchised businesses.

